full_title: I Killed You by Tyler, The Creator
title: I Killed You

description.plain: “I Killed You” centers around the complex relationship Black people have with their hair, navigating a world that often frowns upon natural styles. This pressure leads many to “kill it” by cutting it all off, capturing the struggle between self-identity and societal expectations.
